Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82186,84897}The manager has lost\Nhis gold watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:85231,87483}That man you brought\Nstole the manager's watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:28.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87483,88610}That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88610,91154}I'm talking about Ian!\NThe ex-convict!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92447,94574}No. Don't tell the others about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96701,100413}I will get him jailed,\Nno matter the methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:03.68,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:119182,123686}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,275)}Proving Ian's Innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124646,126689}Ian is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126689,128858}He just sits like this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:14.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128858,134447}and birds from all around come to rest\Non his shoulders and on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135990,138159}From all around?\NHow many of them, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138826,141913}I don't know the exact number,\Nbut there are so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142246,145083}And so we're asking,\Nhow many is "so many"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146751,149587}Ten… No, more like five or six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149587,152340}Oh, that's not too many, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153007,155927}Well, the number\Nmay not be that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155927,158221}But that's not what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:42.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158221,162350}What I meant is that the birds feel\Nat ease around Ian enough to sit on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162934,164060}It's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164060,165395}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165395,166813}Yes. He's like a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166813,170692}When I look at him like that,\Nhe reminds me of a huge tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170692,172985}But isn't he a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173861,176864}I heard from my father\Nthat he robbed a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178491,182578}And people say that he stole\Na gold watch this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:07.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182578,187041}Mom and Dad told me he's dangerous\Nand to stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187041,191129}Scotland Yard came here\Nto catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191963,193172}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:22.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196134,202890}{\i1}Of all the people I have met in my life,\NIan is the most good-natured person so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202890,205893}{\i1}It's tough to be misjudged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206519,208020}It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208730,211524}I don't think Ian is a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211983,214777}I don't think so, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215236,216529}Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216529,218531}Take John's story, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:43.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218531,223911}Birds and animals can tell\Ngood and bad people apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224537,228666}Humans may be tricked,\Nbut you can't fool an animal's instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229917,231794}Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232462,233504}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233504,236174}My Grandpa always told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236174,237008}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237508,239552}Birds don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239552,240303}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240303,241012}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253816,256944}Ian doesn't strike me as the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256944,259614}People can't be judged\Nby their appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283095,284180}Hey, Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284889,288309}You're not a bank robber, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289101,291437}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:55.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291437,295775}But the others won't\Nif you don't say anything, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297109,299862}If they're wrong, just tell them so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:04.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299862,304325}If you explain everything to them,\NI'm sure they'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308663,309997}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309997,312375}That is why I'm working like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315169,316337}Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339068,340903}Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340903,343072}Why don't you listen\Nto my advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343531,344991}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344991,347577}Looks like someone is in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357420,358379}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358713,360172}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360172,362842}Breakfast will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362842,367054}Sorry, but could you deliver lunch\Nto the mine on your way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367430,368556}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368556,370808}No problem, but why two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371267,373269}One's for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373269,374812}The other one's for Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375229,376814}Oh, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377815,381611}But why doesn't Ian\Ntry to defend himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:27.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386824,387742}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:32.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387742,392914}I know you have no problems talking\Nto other people, but what about Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393289,396918}I can't imagine him\Nspeaking much, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:42.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398044,402173}But if he stays that way forever,\Neven I will give up on him sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407094,408596}Listen, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408596,409347}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410056,412224}Your father told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:58.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412224,418147}In spite of all the bad rumors about him,\NIan continued to work hard and didn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418147,420858}It's a proof\Nhe doesn't think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422902,425154}I agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427448,430242}I see. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430993,432328}I understand, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433204,434288}All right, off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434288,435247}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444173,445299}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446425,449136}Good morning, John.\NNice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460064,461816}Hey. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461816,463776}Here, this is your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,465152}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:45.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465152,465861}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465861,469156}Is the other one for Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469156,471951}Yep. Mom made it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471951,473995}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473995,474912}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474912,475579}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476664,479458}Let's make sure people\Ndon't misunderstand Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481669,484964}Good luck, Dad.\NSee you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496183,497351}Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499311,501480}Ian, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502690,504692}Did he go to the forest again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532511,535639}I see, so that is why he had a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546984,548235}That's not Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566837,568172}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570466,571675}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573177,575179}I wonder who that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580351,581894}A button?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592738,594990}All right, put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:59.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595908,599912}I'm sorry you have to live\Nin such a small hut, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600246,601664}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602081,605751}One by one, we'll eventually\Ngather all the necessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605751,607837}As for this junk, we'll throw it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612967,614260}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618180,619181}Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619181,620057}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620808,623644}Ian Copper, 28 years old,\Nborn in Yorkshire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623644,625855}We're going to search your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626272,628774}You are suspected\Nof stealing a gold watch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628774,631110}belonging to Mr. Dohan,\Nthe manager of Wellington Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631652,632444}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634405,635531}Whose watch is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635531,636448}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636824,637741}Is it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637741,638826}No, it's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639326,640536}So who does it belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640536,641662}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641662,643038}I just found it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643038,644915}You found it in this hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644915,647042}In this man's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650045,652298}This might very well be\Nthe stolen watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652298,653841}But Ian did not—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654300,657344}Walter! Bring Mr. Dohan\Nhere immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657344,659430}We're going to ask him\Nfor confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659430,660556}Right away.
Comment: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:06.93,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:666937,666937}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668022,671317}The next king was James I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671317,674695}He was the son of Mary Stuart,\Nknown as the Queen of Scots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674695,677364}When Elizabeth I died in 1603,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677364,679783}she had no children\Nand hadn't named any successor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:23.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679783,683120}thus James had the strongest claim\Nas her first cousin twice removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683120,685873}Oh, that's it! That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685873,686874}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687875,689668}It has my initials here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690586,693422}It's a keepsake\Nafter my late grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693422,695925}It's very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695925,698636}Thank you for your\Ncooperation, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699929,701096}Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702389,703641}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703849,707561}You were absolutely right\Nyesterday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:51.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707561,711232}Mr. Carraclough, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711232,714902}Today, you beat us to the scene\Nand found this crucial piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714902,717404}I can't tell you\Nhow grateful we are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717863,721075}We will take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721075,724912}Who knows? We might as well find\Nevidence of some other crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725162,727748}Such as bank robbery,\Nfor instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727748,729291}Walter, take him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741053,743764}Do not come any closer! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746267,747393}Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748560,749645}Stop it, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749645,751021}Your dog is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751522,754775}Is it wise to let it loose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755234,756110}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:40.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757653,760572}What's the matter?\NI've never seen her like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761699,762866}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762866,765536}Somebody bring me a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773252,776547}What is she doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789810,791937}Lassie hasn't come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791937,794565}She comes here\Nto fetch John every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795107,797067}I wonder if something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797067,797818}Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798444,801363}They came to my house\Nand questioned me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805743,807119}What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807661,809163}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809163,811165}I thought it would\Nturn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811165,812833}Dad, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812833,814251}You could say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814251,817254}The police arrested that man, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817254,818505}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835939,837191}All right, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837191,838650}Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838650,839693}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839693,842696}Isn't it obvious, you oaf?\NYou're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842696,844907}I'll take my time interrogating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844907,847785}Not just about the watch,\Nbut about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848160,850788}Why was that watch\Ninside my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851330,853290}Ha! Because you stole it,\Nthat's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854792,855626}Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:20.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856585,860089}You can't claim that man to be\Ninnocent anymore, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860089,861215}If you excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861215,862216}Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865219,867346}Don't get too close, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867805,870391}There's no telling\Nwhat this scumbag will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871642,873352}I'm not a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874645,875521}Ian…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:41.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876772,881985}You have become close\Nto one hell of a liar, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881985,884071}You have my sympathies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884071,885072}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889910,892037}Get in! Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892037,894665}Dad, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894665,898544}I found the manager's watch\Nin Ian's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899044,901296}Oh, right!\NWhen I was visiting him…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903924,907010}I entered the room\Nand found this button inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907344,908554}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908554,909471}Give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909471,910389}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910389,912599}Don't try to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913100,916603}John, did you enter his room\Nwithout his permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917688,918981}Sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918981,920983}I know it was wrong thing to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920983,923235}But wait till you hear the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923235,925737}What are you doing?\NWe've got no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:30.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925737,930242}Do you think whoever lost this button,\Nplanted the gold watch inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930242,931410}Yes. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931910,934413}John, let Lassie smell the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934788,935747}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939751,940752}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940752,942504}Is the engine acting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942504,943255}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:48.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944047,948260}Lassie, I'm gonna let you free in a second.\NWe're looking for the owner of this button.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950721,952681}Wait a moment. Don't go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952681,954349}– The golden watch—\N– Step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954349,955267}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955267,956727}Never mind him.\NWe're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957644,958979}Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960063,961607}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963650,965402}Good. Everything went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:11.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965402,971116}The criminal the entire British police force\Nis looking for is now in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971116,972951}It's going to be\Na lifetime achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:13.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972951,973827}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981126,982002}It's that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987883,989176}Lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989176,990302}Yes, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999061,1000312}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003690,1005567}Damn it to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005984,1007236}It's the same coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007236,1009071}See? The button is identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:49.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009071,1009988}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009988,1012366}What are you doing\Nwith my luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012366,1013867}Leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015160,1018247}I can't believe how despicable\Nand cowardly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018247,1019540}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019540,1021625}Are you going\Nto badmouth us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021625,1023919}Watch where you tread,\NMr. Carraclough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023919,1027214}or we might have to charge you\Nwith obstruction of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028006,1031593}I'm sure you don't want to let your son\Nsee you in the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031593,1032719}I'm not badmouthing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:15.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034972,1035889}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037015,1038350}What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038684,1042938}It was you who was in Ian's room\Nat that time, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042938,1045983}You went there to plant\NMr. Dohan's gold watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046567,1047651}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053365,1054283}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054283,1056994}I saw everything\Nfrom under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056994,1057786}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057786,1059162}And did you see that man's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059162,1061498}I didn't, but that\Ndoesn't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062124,1064001}I'm afraid it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064001,1065335}Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065335,1069172}How are you raising your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:57.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069172,1077264}Wasn't it you who told me not to\Naccuse others without a definite proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078348,1079516}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079516,1082436}Oh, are you saying that\Nthis is somehow different?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082603,1084521}We have the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084521,1086565}It's your button.\NIt was right in Ian's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088233,1091194}I may have lost it\Nwhen I investigated him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091194,1093655}That doesn't prove anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093655,1095282}Ian stole the gold watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095282,1096366}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097284,1098285}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099077,1100704}Let's drop the pretense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:27.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103081,1107461}It doesn't feel right\Nto seize him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108045,1110547}Walter! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:34.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110547,1114676}Ian has a criminal record.\NHe stole money from the national bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114676,1116428}And what is in\Nthat criminal record?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:41.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116428,1121016}He only injured somebody\Nin an accident due to negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121016,1123226}– What? Just an accident?\N– That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123644,1126730}I thought it was a robbery\Nor a homicide, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126730,1128231}It was just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:54.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128690,1134237}Besides, we suspected that the bank robbery\Nwas working as part of a gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134529,1136031}Silence, Walter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136615,1138533}No. I won't stay silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138533,1141078}Ian didn't steal any gold watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142746,1146958}You found it in the drawer\Nin Mr. Dohan's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146958,1150379}You went into Ian's room\Nand put it there yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152547,1155217}I see.\NSo that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155217,1156093}Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173110,1174403}Let's go, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176863,1178407}We're going back\Nto the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178407,1179449}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179449,1180992}Ian Copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180992,1184121}Don't think\NI'm letting you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184121,1185706}I'm not the type that gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185706,1187290}Get the cuffs off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187290,1188166}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192337,1193714}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193714,1194464}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194923,1196299}What are you doing, Walter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196299,1197718}Get in the car already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197718,1200595}Don't make me lose my temper\Nany more, you worthless punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200595,1202472}Yes sir. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212149,1214484}Well done, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214484,1216319}It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222200,1225328}The gang of bank robbers\Nwere caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225704,1226997}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226997,1229207}– That's a load off my mind.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:33.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229207,1233086}This means Ian shouldn't have\Nany more trouble with the law enforcers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234254,1236173}I feel so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:40.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236173,1240385}Because of me,\NIan went through so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240385,1243847}Do you think he will still\Nwant to work here at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245056,1246600}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246850,1250604}I told you from the start\Nthat Ian can't be the bank robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250604,1252230}I trusted him all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252230,1255358}You just say whatever\Npops in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266995,1269623}Wait! I want to see him, too!
